Package: distro-defaults
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: set various default options
 This package has much influence on the system and update behaviour of
 customized live Linux utilities. It is dynamically created at distro build
 time.

Package: fll-live-initscripts
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, 
 adduser,
 console-setup (>= 1.47),
 cpufrequtils,
 distro-defaults,
 eject,
 fll-live-utils,
 ifplugd,
 ceni,
 keyboard-configuration (>= 1.47),
 lsb-base (>= 3.0-6),
 sysvinit-utils (>= 2.86.ds1-64)
Recommends: tzdata
Conflicts: kdm (<< 4:4.2.2-2), slim (<< 1.3.1)
Description: fll live media sysv initscripts
 A set of initscripts suitable for managing the SysV-Init boot sequence of the
 live media generated by code from the F.U.L.L.S.T.O.R.Y project.

Package: fll-live-xorgconfig
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, 
 distro-defaults,
 perl,
 lsb-base (>= 3.0-6),
 xserver-xorg-core (>= 2:1.6.1)
Recommends: kdm | gdm, xserver-xorg-input-vmmouse (>> 12.6.3)
Conflicts: libdrm-nouveau1,
 xserver-xorg-video-all,
 xserver-xorg-video-nouveau
Description: fll live media xorg related tools
 A set of scripts to generate a Xorg configuration.

Package: fll-live-utils
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, 
 udev
Description: fll live utilities
 A set of tools for use by fll-live-initscripts.
